    <br>
    <p style="text-align: justify;">In the event of a Chargeback situation arising in case of any Products purchased by a User/ Payer, for which payment has been made to the Payee/User / Service Provider, the User/ Payer shall be advised to resolve the issue with the Payee/User / Service Provider at the earliest and shall then settle the payment in accordance with the solution agreed upon by the Parties only if the Payee refunds the amounts back .</p>
